4. cs.CE (Computational Engineering, Finance, and Science) - The paper discusses the application of optimization solvers to real-world problems, which is a common topic in computational engineering and science. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper proposes a new method of problem decomposition for solving the maximum clique problem, which could be relevant to the field of systems and control.
